  "body": "I've updated the diagnostic registration plugin so that it validates error descriptions. An error description is only valid if it starts and ends with a newline, and contains no more than 80 characters per line.\n\nThe plugin forced me to fix E0005 and E0006 which had escaped manual attention!\n\nI've also added errors for E0267, E0268, E0296, whilst updating E0303 as per discussion in #24143.\n\ncc #24407\n",
